ing-al-nudhr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8DY","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":34533,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/01\/god-fearing-overcome-steep\/","url_meta":{"origin":33230,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Fear: Only God-fearing will overcome the steep path","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 1, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, before you is a burdensome path to traverse. No one is saved from it except everyone who fears falling into sin.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Bazza\u0304r 4118 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u064e\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":30378,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/20\/easy-spoils-fasting-winter-days\/","url_meta":{"origin":33230,"position":1},"title":"Abu Huraira on Fasting: Easy spoils by fasting short winter days","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu'aym reported: Abu Huraira, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I tell you about easy spoils?\u201d They said, \u201cO Abu Huraira, what are they?\u201d Abu Huraira said, \u201cFasting in the winter.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 1356 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0646\u0639\u064a\u0645 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e